---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { url } from '../utils/url';
---
<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn about Zava Insurance's mission, vision, values, and our commitment to community ‚Äî protecting families since 1987.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero hero--page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Zava Insurance</h1>
      <p>Since 1987, we've been more than an insurance company ‚Äî we've been a trusted neighbor protecting the people and places that matter most.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div>
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>Zava Insurance was founded in 1987 by Maria and Eduardo Zava in Hartford, Connecticut. What started as a small family-owned agency with a single office and a commitment to honest service has grown into one of the region's most respected insurance providers.</p>
          <p>Eduardo, a first-generation immigrant from Portugal, understood what it meant to build something from nothing. He believed that everyone ‚Äî regardless of background ‚Äî deserved access to reliable protection for their families, homes, and livelihoods.</p>
          <p>Today, Zava Insurance serves over 250,000 policyholders across 12 branch locations, while still honoring the personal touch that Maria and Eduardo built into every interaction. The company is now led by their daughter, Sofia Zava-Mitchell, who carries forward the family's legacy of trust, integrity, and community service.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="two-col__image">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366216548-37526070297c?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Zava Insurance headquarters building" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="section section--gray" id="mission">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="two-col" style="gap: 3rem;">
        <div class="two-col__image">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521791136064-7986c2920216?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Team collaboration at Zava Insurance" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-navy); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">"To provide accessible, reliable, and compassionate insurance solutions that empower individuals, families, and businesses to live with confidence and security."</p>
          <p>We believe that protection shouldn't be a luxury. Every policy we write is backed by a promise to stand beside our clients in their most challenging moments ‚Äî whether it's a fender bender, a house fire, or a medical emergency.</p>
          <p>Our mission drives every decision we make, from the products we design to the communities we serve. We measure our success not just by policies sold, but by the families we help recover, the businesses we keep running, and the peace of mind we deliver.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Vision -->
  <section class="section" id="vision">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="two-col" style="gap: 3rem;">
        <div>
          <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-navy); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">"To be the most trusted and community-centered insurance company in America, setting the standard for ethical practices, innovation, and client care."</p>
          <p>We envision a future where every person has access to the protection they need, delivered with transparency and empathy. We're investing in technology to make insurance simpler, faster, and more personalized ‚Äî while never losing the human connection that defines Zava.</p>
          <p>By 2030, our goal is to expand to 25 branch locations, launch fully digital policy management, and double our community investment through the Zava Cares Foundation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="two-col__image">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Planning the future of Zava Insurance" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section section--gray" id="values">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
        <p>The principles that guide every interaction, every policy, and every decision at Zava Insurance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-grid">
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-item__icon">ü§ù</span>
          <h3>Integrity First</h3>
          <p>We do what's right, even when no one is watching. Transparent pricing, honest advice, and ethical practices are non-negotiable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-item__icon">üíõ</span>
          <h3>Compassionate Service</h3>
          <p>Behind every policy is a person. We listen, empathize, and go the extra mile ‚Äî especially when our clients need us most.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-item__icon">üåç</span>
          <h3>Community Commitment</h3>
          <p>We grow where we're planted. Supporting local causes, volunteering, and investing in neighborhoods is part of our DNA.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-item__icon">üî¨</span>
          <h3>Innovation</h3>
          <p>We embrace technology and new ideas to make insurance simpler, faster, and more accessible for everyone.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-item__icon">üìà</span>
          <h3>Excellence</h3>
          <p>From underwriting to claims, we hold ourselves to the highest standards. Continuous improvement is our culture.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-item__icon">üåà</span>
          <h3>Inclusivity</h3>
          <p>We celebrate diversity and ensure our products, workplace, and services are welcoming and accessible to all.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Community Impact -->
  <section class="section" id="community">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Community Impact</h2>
        <p>We believe in building stronger communities ‚Äî one initiative at a time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="two-col" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <div class="two-col__image">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559027615-cd4628902d4a?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Zava Insurance community volunteer day" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Zava Cares Foundation</h3>
          <p>Established in 2005, the Zava Cares Foundation is the heart of our community engagement. Each year, we invest over <strong>$2 million</strong> in programs that strengthen the neighborhoods we serve.</p>
          <ul style="color: var(--color-gray-600); padding-left: 1.25rem;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Disaster Relief Fund</strong> ‚Äî Rapid-response support for communities affected by natural disasters, providing emergency housing and essentials.</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Zava Scholars Program</strong> ‚Äî $500,000 in annual scholarships for first-generation college students pursuing degrees in finance, healthcare, and community service.</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Financial Literacy Workshops</strong> ‚Äî Free community workshops teaching budgeting, insurance basics, and retirement planning.</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Home Safety Initiative</strong> ‚Äî Free home safety inspections and smoke detector installations for low-income families.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <div class="icon-card">
          <span class="icon-card__icon">üéì</span>
          <h3>$5M+ in Scholarships</h3>
          <p>Awarded since 2005, helping over 2,000 students achieve their educational dreams.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-card">
          <span class="icon-card__icon">ü§≤</span>
          <h3>15,000+ Volunteer Hours</h3>
          <p>Contributed annually by Zava employees through paid volunteer days and community events.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-card">
          <span class="icon-card__icon">üèòÔ∏è</span>
          <h3>50+ Partner Nonprofits</h3>
          <p>Local organizations we support through funding, volunteering, and pro-bono services.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Leadership -->
  <section class="section section--gray" id="leadership">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Leadership Team</h2>
        <p>Meet the people driving Zava Insurance's mission forward.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--4">
        <div class="card">
          <img class="card__image" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face" alt="Sofia Zava-Mitchell, CEO" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3>Sofia Zava-Mitchell</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--color-teal); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Chief Executive Officer</p>
            <p>Carrying on the family legacy with 18 years in insurance leadership and a passion for innovation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img class="card__image" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560250097-0b93528c311a?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face" alt="David Park, COO" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3>David Park</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--color-teal); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Chief Operating Officer</p>
            <p>Operations veteran with 20+ years scaling insurance companies while maintaining service excellence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img class="card__image" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face" alt="Amara Johnson, CFO" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3>Amara Johnson</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--color-teal); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Chief Financial Officer</p>
            <p>Financial strategist ensuring Zava's growth and stability with an A+ AM Best rating.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img class="card__image" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face" alt="Marcus Rivera, CTO" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3>Marcus Rivera</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--color-teal); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Chief Technology Officer</p>
            <p>Leading Zava's digital transformation with AI-powered tools and seamless client experiences.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Want to Be Part of the Zava Family?</h2>
      <p>We're always looking for passionate people to join our team and help protect communities.</p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href={url('/careers')} class="btn btn--gold btn--lg">View Open Positions</a>
        <a href={url('/life-at-zava')} class="btn btn--outline-white btn--lg">Life at Zava</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
